    General Stores in Girgaon, Mumbai

    (381 Ratings & Reviews) 4.0 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Girgaon, Mumbai

    General stores or mom-n-pop shops are known as 'kiranas' in most parts of the country. In marketing terminology, a kirana shop is a form of traditional retail catering to the needs of citizens. In certain metros and cities, a general store can also be a part of a pharmacy or medicine shop. These retail stores are a part of the sales network of most FMCG brands and leading manufacturing companies. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. Please scroll up to find a list of General Stores in Girgaon, Mumbai.
